        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", edit. 1866). The ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "kingdom",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " of Hamath comprised the tract of this valley of the Orontes, skirted by the hills separating the Leontes from the Orontes, and extending to the Pass of Daphne below Antioch. ",
