        "text": "2 Kings 23:33",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") lies on the east bank of the Orontes, thirty-five miles north-east of Baal-bek, or Baal-gad. The people of Hamath were of the race of Ham, of the descendants of Canaan (",
